  "3023690": {
    "name": "Money And Lady | 财貌双全",
    "steam_appid": 3023690,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023690/extras/6bec87b6af368ae5af26c1bea6e6f0fd.avif?t=1734525043\" width=600 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎大家关注我们的Steam游戏社区 我们会在Steam游戏社区提供游戏相关帮助，游戏补丁，以及活动更新 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >4K高清 额外 5.6G免费H补丁！绅士大富翁！你不冲吗？！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们的游戏玩法简单又有趣！搞笑又可爱！多姿多彩滴HHHHHHHHHA哈~ 希望我的作品可以给大家带来快乐~希望大家愿意支持我们的正版游戏！ 给我们继续更新它的力量吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你懂得： Steam 商店搜索 HAPPY BOOM PATCH </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >或者关注 YOUTUBE，DISCORD，ITCH 来找到相关信息</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023690/extras/7cdca26c37165d038f0f82961c4a2ada.avif?t=1734525043\" width=600 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >首先！你必须通过掷骰子来移动你的角色，当然你的骰子是可以通过载具的升级而变化的哟~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中骰子有许多类型：4,6,8,10,12,20面骰子</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023690/extras/1e61a2c1ae447f4640bc42e6f2e589c2.avif?t=1734525043\" width=600 height=160 /></span>游戏目前拥有11名可选择角色（7位主角，3位被封印的角色，1位隐藏角色），</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以及6名为大家辛苦服务的NPC，共计17名动态角色</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023690/extras/587262b20297fe8f6fb1214e068397db.avif?t=1734525043\" width=600 height=160 /></span>游戏中 基本地产 和 商业 是有区别的，可以通过增加星星来提高等级和收益</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地产：收益固定</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >商业：收益不稳定，但可以在对手休息的时候依然赚到金币！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你在同一区域拥有的地产或商业越多，那么会获得额外的收益加成！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023690/extras/c6fc66924fb346d4301589d6c832f5ff.avif?t=1734525043\" width=600 height=160 /></span>钱多的时候可以考虑，争夺黄金区域！它拥有7种不同类型的建筑等待大家去改建</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超级市场：赚点大钱！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >风景：有概率触发闪电！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >神庙：定期提供庇护</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >科研所：定期送你一些奇怪的道具</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >娱乐城：在这里赚钱或者赔钱全看运气咯！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >电影院：让对手休息一下！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >同时，黄金区域也可以被大家投票，当投票集满时，黄金区域将会被强制拆除！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >黄金区域的所有者回到黄金区域时可以减少投票的次数！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023690/extras/a24bc563ea83b03960b4dc548e5bf61a.avif?t=1734525043\" width=600 height=160 /></span>有30多种道具等待着大家去获得</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中合理的规划并使用道具可是让你快速成功的关键哟~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023690/extras/7f7033f14556a0f0348bbef3162fc046.avif?t=1734525043\" width=600 height=160 /></span>游戏中有30多种不同的随机事件，这些事件往往伴随着：悲伤！快乐！疯狂！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还有一些情况也能触发随机事件：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023690/extras/0b8862eaf2272cb878d588f447d92e6e.avif?t=1734525043\" width=600 height=160 /></span>如果你进入了修道院，那么修女可以免费的为你做一些魔幻的祷告！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你进入的是魔法屋，神秘魔法师的施法可不是免费的！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023690/extras/fb1f2307c7c02653501d38df0302512e.avif?t=1734525043\" width=600 height=160 /></span>美少女俱乐部！作为绅士的大家肯定非常熟悉啦！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这里每过10天都会举行幸运女明星选举！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你应援的美少女成为了幸运女明星！那么你就会得到高额的奖金哟！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中有20位美少女等待着大家去应援哟！（还有10位隐藏美少女等待着大家去找寻哟）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023690/extras/2e3764a9c5026ec84e00be391dfdcdb4.avif?t=1734525043\" width=600 height=160 /></span>商店当然是必不可少的！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >商店中包含特价商品、盲盒、以及普通商品！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >商店虽好！但千万别冲动消费呀！小心破产！~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023690/extras/7e397c590cb165dc2a838361060dcbd6.avif?t=1734525043\" width=600 height=160 /></span>游戏目前包含3个主要地图： </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小型地图—FC自由城</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >中型地图—香薰岛</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大型地图—咚不啦城</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个地图的大小，玩法，策略都有区别，还有各种不同的地图遭遇等待着大家呢！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023690/extras/34e8a740faa9193ac97e350dd94768fe.avif?t=1734525043\" width=600 height=160 /></span>作为地产经营类派对游戏，胜利条件当然是设定好“胜利天数”或者“让其他竞争者都破产”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但如果大家可以得到美少女们的青睐当然也很成功啦！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所以，不要太在意胜利条件嘛！~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023690/extras/d6727e553dc5fd3946fa8d630d4d9a3a.avif?t=1734525043\" width=600 height=160 /></span>支持本地联机（最多4人）以及和美少女AI一起游玩~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >因为贫穷和技术的原因，目前实在是做不出来网络联机功能，抱歉~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果想网络联机可以借助Steam远程同乐功能或者在线会议软件来进行联机~</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >有爱的CV们</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >感谢我们强大的声优阵容： </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Q星  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yuuna Kyuuta - 由依结月 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >火火子  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Iona Fujita 藤田伊緒奈</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >银珠 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Naoka Nakayama 中山尚華</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >蕾丝  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Miyuki Nishimura 宫崎美雪</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >柠檬 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Naoka Nakayama 中山尚華</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >琳 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ayana Nagafuchi 永渕文菜</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小卡拉蜜 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Haruna Suzuki 鈴木春菜</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >奇美拉 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Juliana Ayumi Misaki </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >三崎ジュリアナあゆみ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >三崎朱莉安娜步</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玛露丽 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Saho Taoka 田岡佐穂</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >赛博喵喵 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Akina Kato 嘉藤明奈</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >俱乐部女仆 奥丽莎  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mio Nakai  中井美桜 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >播报员 卡拉  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Asaka Yamazaki 山崎朝香</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >修女 波丽   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ayaka Oonishi 大西爱香</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >工程师 王佳欣  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Miyuki Matsui 松井宫子</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >店铺老板 桃井甜绘  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Touko Murakami 村上桃子</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >占卜师 李智希 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Suzuka Hashino 桥野铃花</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >？？？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Soran Takei 武井宙舞</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Saho Taoka 田岡佐穂</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >最后 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >希望大家多多支持哟~ 真心希望您可以支持我们，购买我们的正版游戏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拒绝！拒绝！拒绝盗版游戏！您的支持是我们的继续更新的动力！爱你！BiuBiuBiu~♥</p>",
